**DOC-05  ·  Information Architecture ****&**** Screen Inventory — v1.2**

Version 1.0  ·  Confidential  ·  June 2026

# **CHANGE NOTICE — v1.1 → v1.2**

| **Source: Onboarding prototype analysis + founder feedback on long-press gesture** **Screens added to MVP:** OB-00: Conversational intro — stats engagement screen before first onboarding question OB-08b: Single-day plan preview — today's 3 meals shown at end of onboarding (bridges to H-01) **Screens updated:** OB-03: Now includes migration duration slider — feeds RE city overlay weight calculation OB-07: Left/right card swipe with visible action buttons replaces vertical class thumbnail swipe **Gesture system — breaking change:** Long-press + drag REMOVED from entire product — was not discoverable or intuitive REPLACED: swipe left on card reveals Not Today (amber) and Never (red) action buttons Carousel now accessed via tap on swap icon in action bar — left swipe is reserved for action reveal Screen count: 35 (up from 33). Flow 1 and Flow 3 updated. |
