# **03  Universal screen states — unchanged**

| **State** | **What shows** | **Applies to** |
| --- | --- | --- |
| **Loading** | Skeleton placeholder matching content shape | All data-dependent screens |
| **Populated** | Full content rendered | All screens |
| **Empty** | Illustration + text + primary CTA. Never blank white. | H-01, W-01, MM-01, S-02, P-05 |
| **Error** | Error message + retry button | All data-dependent screens |
| **Offline (cached)** | Offline banner. Cached content. Network actions disabled. | H-01, H-09, W-01 |
| **Offline (no cache)** | Offline illustration + connect prompt | H-01 (new user, never loaded) |
| **Constraint conflict** | Friendly message + link to edit profile | H-01 (RE returns empty slate) |

