# **05  Critical user flow maps (v1.2)**

**v1.2: **Flow 1 updated (OB-00, OB-08b added). Flow 3 updated (swipe-reveal replaces long-press).

## **Flow 1 — New user to first plan (UPDATED)**

| **Step** | **Screen** | **User action** | **System output** |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| **1** | **A-02 Welcome** | Taps Get started | Navigate to A-03 Sign up |
| **2** | **A-03 Sign up** | Enters email + password | Account created. Navigate to OB-00. |
| **3** | **OB-00 Conversational intro** | Reads: '1,095 meal decisions a year — we'll take those off your plate.' Taps Continue. | No data collected. Pure engagement. Navigate to OB-01. |
| **4** | **OB-01 Cohort** | Selects Family with kids | MC_FAMILY. Navigate to OB-02 kids branch. |
| **5** | **OB-02 Household** | Selects school child age bands (ages 8 and 5) | member_segments = [SCHOOL_CHILD]. OB-03. |
| **6** | **OB-03 State + city + duration** | Selects Madhya Pradesh, Pune, 3–7 years in city | home_state, current_city, migration_years stored. RE city overlay weight = medium. OB-04. |
| **7** | **OB-04 to OB-07** | Completes diet, allergens, cook capability, dish swipes | All preference signals stored. OB-08. |
| **8** | **OB-08 Profile** | Enters name Meera, sets 7 AM notification | Profile stored. RE generates plan in background. Navigate to OB-08b. |
| **9** | **OB-08b Plan preview** | Sees today's 3 meal cards — the first view of the AI's work. Taps swap on lunch. Selects alternative. Taps Looks good! | Plan confirmed. Navigate to H-01 with same plan pre-loaded. |
| **10** | **H-01 Day View** | Full Day View with tab bar. Same plan from preview. | Onboarding complete. First session active. |

## **Flow 2 — Daily use loop (unchanged — see v1.1)**

Flow 2 unchanged from v1.1.

## **Flow 3a — Not Today (UPDATED — swipe-reveal)**

| **Step** | **Screen** | **User action** | **System output** |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| **1** | **H-01 Day View** | Swipes left on lunch meal card | Card slides 80px left. Not Today (amber) and Never (red) buttons emerge from right edge. |
| **2** | **H-01 action revealed** | Taps Not Today (amber, clock icon) | H-06 bottom sheet: dish name + Skip today / Cancel |
| **3** | **H-06 Not Today sheet** | Taps Skip today | Sheet closes. Card snaps back. Slot regenerates. Toast: Lunch skipped for today. |
| **4** | **RE background** | Event: dish_not_today logged | Penalty P(t) = 0.80 × e^(-0.35t) applied. Dish returns to normal in ~7 days. |

## **Flow 3b — Never (UPDATED — swipe-reveal)**

| **Step** | **Screen** | **User action** | **System output** |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| **1** | **H-01 Day View** | Swipes left on dinner meal card | Not Today + Never buttons emerge. |
| **2** | **H-01 action revealed** | Taps Never (red, trash icon) | H-07 bottom sheet: dish photo + Remove forever / Cancel |
| **3** | **H-07 Never sheet** | Taps Remove forever | Sheet closes. Toast: [Dish] removed. Slot regenerates immediately. |
| **4** | **RE background** | Event: dish_never logged | Dish added to never_list. Excluded from all future candidate sets permanently. |

